# Mondy, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Mondy (; , Moondo) is a rural locality (a settlement) in Tunkinsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 1,000 as of 2010. There are 18 streets.
Geography
Mondy is located 84&nbsp;km west of Kyren (the district's administrative centre) by road. Turan is the nearest rural locality.
